title: From Dr. Boyce to Your Voice
itunes:title: From Dr. Boyce to Your Voice
description:
THU 6/9 - Dr. Boyce Watkins sits down with The Breakfast Club to discuss everything from Muhammad Ali's image after death to securing your financial future. Then it's your turn to speak as "Ask Yee" provides an opportunity for you to vent about relationship drama, saving you money on a different kind of doctor.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
